§ 467o. Repealed. Pub. L. 118–272, div. A, title I, § 1132(e), Jan. 4, 2025, 138 Stat. 3024
Section, Pub. L. 92–367, § 15, as added Pub. L. 117–263, div. H, title LXXXI, § 8122, Dec. 23, 2022, 136 Stat. 3713, related to national low-head dam inventory. See section 467d of this title.
